@NODE Introduction "EasyElements Hypertext Manual - Introduction"

@{u}Introduction@{uu}

EasyElements is a small utility (18 k) for chemical elements.
Enter either an element, an atomic symbol or an atomic number and EasyElements will output the element name, atomic symbol, atomic number, atomic weight, specific gravity, melting point (in C°), boiling point (in C°) and year of discovery.

@ENDNODE

