@NODE Usage "EasyElements Hypertext Manual - Usage"

@{u}Usage@{uu}

Using EasyElements is really easy!  Start it by clicking on its icon, or alternatively enter its name in a Shell.
A window with one string gadget and some text (read only) gadgets will appear.  Enter either an element (e.g. actinium), a symbol (e.g. Ac) or an atomic number (e.g. 89) and EasyElements will automatically update the read only gadgets.
If your input was incorrect, EasyElements will clear all text gadgets.

@ENDNODE

